Package de.coderarea.jrdp.protocol.MCS Description

Multipoint Communication Service Protocol.
Encoding: BER - using BinaryNotes lib
Encoding: PER - using own implementation
The files in subpackage BN_BER package have been generated using the BinaryNotes compiler.
Author:
Sascha Biedermann
